description:
Today on the show, its only right they started off the show with Kendrick Lamar's new song "The Heart part 5". Next we had friend to the room Ja Rule stop by where he spoke about ICONN, Murder Inc Documentary, Parenting, Harvard Business Degree and more They also had Marc Lamont Hill stop by where he spoke about his new book "Seen and Unseen", how visual media shifting the narrative,  the skepticals of death and more.
